{
  "texts": [
    "This work presented an approach that decomposes a written essay and extract hierarchical discourse structure and organization from essays that can be utilized as a feedback for coherent flow of ideas.",
    "Han et al. (2023a) proposed a Feedback generation guided with AES By Rubric-based dataset Incorporating ChatGPT (FABRIC), which is capable of essay scoring and feedback generation.",
    "FABRIC combines both essay scoring and feedback generation in the AES task.",
    "Fabric has three main components, namely DREsS, CASE, and EssayCoT, which addresses different AES task problems.",
    "DREsS is a rubric-based dataset where the traits are content, organization, and language."
  ]
}